::KitKat2::
She was running at high speed, enjoying her freedom.  She was just 
crossing a river, when everything when black.  She woke up a mile 
down river, on the side of the river bank.  She slowly got up and 
walked a few feet, then fell to the ground.  She closed her eyes and 
tried to think of what just happened.  She lay there, feeling an 
immence pain in her head. She transformed into bot mode and sat down 
on the side of the river. "I must have hit a rock when I wasn't 
looking."  She glanced around, but saw only trees around her. "And 
where am I now? I must have floated here, but where's here?"

She stood up, putting her hand to her forehead, and started to walk 
onlong what looked like a path. It lead to the Allience base.


::KitKat3::
She woke up and shook her head.  "OUCH! That hurt like the pit. What 
happened?"  She looked around, but saw no other bots in sight.  She 
sniffed, but only caught her own scent.  She decided to keep going.  
She walked along, hoping to make it to the base soon.
